                            <incipit><locus>F. 1(ka)b</locus>
                                Namo tassa ...
                                Mahā kāruṇikaṃ nāthaṃ ñeyyam sāgara pāraguṃ
                                vande nipunaṃ gambhīraṃ vicitta naya desanaṃ
                                yanu heyin mē Vimānavastu-prakaraṇaya karannā vū Mahā-vihāravāsi vū 
                                tripiṭaka-dhārī Dharmapāla nam mahā-shavirayan visin prakaraṇārambhayaṭa
                                paḷamuva iṣṭa-devatā namaskāra vasayen ...
                            </incipit>
                            <explicit><locus>F. 125 (jo)a</locus>
                                Sat-veni sunikkhitta vargaya kiyā nimavana-ladi. Tavada mē
                                Vimānavastu-prakaraṇayehi, Sīhala bhāsa katṛūn visin saṇgraha
                                karana-lada śāsanopakāra saṅgraha vastuva nam kavara-yat. Purātana paṭan mūla-bhaṣāyayi
                                kiyana-lada Pāli artha vasayen pāvata āvā-vū mē Vimānavastu prakaraṇayehi ...
                                mē heḷu Vimānavastu-prakaraṇaya ... apa visin saṅgraha karana ladu-va
                                prakāṣakoṭa dakvamha.
                            </explicit>
